---
layout: layouts/base.njk
permalink: /panier/index.html
title: "Mon panier"
description: "Récapitulatif de votre panier — VapeLab, boutique CBD &amp; Vape à Gex (01170)"
---
{# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
   panier.njk — Page panier
   ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── #}

<section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-10 lg:py-16">

  {# Fil d'Ariane #}
  <nav aria-label="Fil d'Ariane" class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-6 text-xs font-mono fade-up">
    <a href="/" class="breadcrumb-link">Accueil</a>
    <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-dark-border" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8.25 4.5l7.5 7.5-7.5 7.5"/></svg>
    <span class="text-neon-green">Mon panier</span>
  </nav>

  <h1 class="font-display text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-white tracking-wide mb-3 fade-up">MON PANIER</h1>
  <p class="text-smoke text-sm mb-10 fade-up">Vérifiez votre commande avant de continuer.</p>

  {# ─── État vide (caché par défaut) ─────────────────────────────────── #}
  <div id="cart-empty" class="hidden text-center py-20 rounded-2xl border border-dashed border-dark-border bg-dark-card/40">
    <div class="text-5xl mb-4">🛒</div>
    <h3 class="font-display text-2xl text-white mb-2">Votre panier est vide</h3>
    <p class="text-smoke text-sm max-w-md mx-auto mb-6">
      Ajoutez des produits depuis nos univers — CBD, Vape, Puffs, Chicha, Accessoires.
    </p>
    <a href="/" class="btn-neon-green inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 rounded-xl text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">
      Découvrir la boutique
    </a>
  </div>

  {# ─── Contenu panier (rempli en JS) ───────────────────────────────── #}
  <div id="cart-content" class="hidden lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

    {# Colonne gauche : liste des items #}
    <div class="lg:col-span-2">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
        <span class="text-smoke text-sm font-mono" id="cart-count-label"></span>
        <button id="cart-clear-btn"
                class="text-xs text-smoke hover:text-red-400 transition-colors flex items-center gap-1 font-mono"
                aria-label="Vider le panier">
          <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M14.74 9l-.346 9m-4.788 0L9.26 9m9.968-3.21c.342.052.682.107 1.022.166m-1.022-.165L18.16 19.673a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.244 2.077H8.084a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.244-2.077L4.772 5.79m14.456 0a48.108 48.108 0 00-3.478-.397m-12 .562c.34-.059.68-.114 1.022-.165m0 0a48.11 48.11 0 013.478-.397m7.5 0v-.916c0-1.18-.91-2.164-2.09-2.201a51.964 51.964 0 00-3.32 0c-1.18.037-2.09 1.022-2.09 2.201v.916m7.5 0a48.667 48.667 0 00-7.5 0"/></svg>
          Vider le panier
        </button>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-3" id="cart-items">
        {# Items injectés par JS — voir tabacgex.js initCartPage() #}
      </div>
    </div>

    {# Colonne droite : récap + CTA (sticky desktop) #}
    <aside class="lg:sticky lg:top-24 self-start">
      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-dark-card border border-dark-border p-6">
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl tracking-widest text-white mb-5">RÉCAPITULATIF</h2>

        <dl class="space-y-3 text-sm">
          <div class="flex justify-between">
            <dt class="text-smoke">Sous-total HT</dt>
            <dd class="font-mono text-white" id="cart-total-ht">0,00 €</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between">
            <dt class="text-smoke">TVA (20 %)</dt>
            <dd class="font-mono text-white" id="cart-total-tva">0,00 €</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="flex justify-between pt-3 border-t border-dark-border">
            <dt class="font-display text-base tracking-wider text-white">TOTAL TTC</dt>
            <dd class="font-display text-2xl" style="color:#39FF14;" id="cart-total-ttc">0,00 €</dd>
          </div>
        </dl>

        <div class="my-5 p-3 rounded-xl border border-neon-blue/20 bg-neon-blue/5 flex gap-2 text-xs">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 shrink-0 mt-0.5" style="color:#00D4FF;" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 10.5a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 10.5c0 7.142-7.5 11.25-7.5 11.25S4.5 17.642 4.5 10.5a7.5 7.5 0 1115 0z"/></svg>
          <span class="text-smoke">
            <strong class="text-white">Click &amp; Collect gratuit</strong> — Retrait en boutique au 48 Rue de Genève, Gex.
          </span>
        </div>

        <a href="/commande/" id="cart-checkout-btn"
           class="btn-neon-green w-full py-4 rounded-xl text-sm uppercase tracking-widest flex items-center justify-center gap-2.5 font-bold">
          Continuer la commande
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5 21 12m0 0-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"/></svg>
        </a>

        <a href="/" class="block mt-3 text-center text-smoke text-xs hover:text-white transition-colors underline underline-offset-2">
          Continuer mes achats
        </a>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>

{# Données produits exposées au JS pour ré-hydrater le panier #}
<script id="produits-data" type="application/json">
{{ produits | dump | safe }}
</script>
